title: Apocrathia's Ringtone Collection
description:
This is a custom made set of ringtones that I keep on my phone, all of them were ripped from various locations and edited using Adobe Audition 2.0.

Heres a quick list for you all:
the badgerbadgerbadger song
banana phone
bleach&#039;s season 1 intro music.
final fantasy vii - fanfare
final fantasy vii - prelude
galaga
hello infidel
our lady peace - somewhere out there
pacman
powerpuff girls jingle
rickroll
sonic - title screen music
streets of rage - character select music
zelda - link to the past - overworld theme

so i hope you enjoy these, its given my phone something a bit different than the same billboard top 40 ringtones that everyone else has. they turn heads, piss people off, and may make you seem like a total geek.
